Contact Details: Author: Screening & Immunisations Team, NHS Digital Responsible Statistician: Sally Jones Email enquiries@nhsdigital.nhs.uk Telephone 0300 303 5678
Description: This report presents provisional statistics summarising the NHS Breast Screening Programme in England in 2017-18. It includes data on the number of women invited for breast screening, coverage, uptake of invitations and cancers detected. National level data is presented in the report.
Name: Breast Screening Programme
Route from landing page to data: Data can be located by clicking on the link under latest version.  Scroll down to resources and 3 CSV file are located in the Zip file.
